edu.uga.dawgtrades.model

Interface RegisteredUser

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Persistable

    public interface RegisteredUser
extends Persistable
    This interface represents a RegisteredUser of DawgTrades. It has a collection of methods to read/write RegisteredUser's attributes. It also extends the Persistable interface, since objects of this class will be stored in the persistent data store. * @author Krys J. Kochut
